var e=[{id:`L3_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`SIGMA_RAS_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`와아, 사람 정말 많다!`,JPN:`わあ、人がいっぱい！`,ENG:`Wow! Look at all these people!`,TWN:`哇，好多人喔！`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`SIGMA_RAS_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_LAUGH`},R:null}}},{id:`L4_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`SIGMA_RAS_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`아빠, 저 사람들 모두 아빠 직원이 되는 거야?`,JPN:`パパ、あの人たちがみんなパパの会社の社員になるの？`,ENG:`Daddy, are all these people gonna work for you?`,TWN:`爸爸，他們都會成為爸爸的員工嗎？`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`SIGMA_RAS_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_IDLE`},R:null}}},{id:`L6_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`USER_ADMIN_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`하하, 그러면 좋겠구나.`,JPN:`ハハ、そうだったらいいね。`,ENG:`Haha, I wish that was the case.`,TWN:`哈哈，那樣當然是最好的。`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`SIGMA_RAS_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_IDLE`},R:null}}},{id:`L7_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`USER_ADMIN_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`지금 있는 언니 오빠들을 도와 주려면 아주 훌륭한 사람들이 필요해.`,JPN:`今いるお姉さんとお兄さんたちを助けてあげるためには、とても立派な人たちが必要なんだ。`,ENG:`But we can only afford to have the best to help our company.`,TWN:`必須是很厲害的人，才能幫得上哥哥姊姊們。`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`SIGMA_RAS_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_IDLE`},R:null}}},{id:`L8_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`USER_ADMIN_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`저 중에서 그런 사람들을 찾을 수 있게 시그마도 도와 주겠니?`,JPN:`あの中からそんな人を探せるように、シグマも手伝ってくれるかい？`,ENG:`So, will you help me find those kinds of people, Sigma?`,TWN:`西格瑪可以一起幫忙從那些人當中找到合適的人嗎？`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`SIGMA_RAS_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_IDLE`},R:null}}},{id:`L9_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`SIGMA_RAS_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`응! 걱정 마, 아빠! 나한테 맡겨!`,JPN:`うん！　心配しないで、パパ！　私に任せて！`,ENG:`Okay! Leave it to me, Daddy!`,TWN:`可以！爸爸放心！交給我！`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`SIGMA_RAS_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_PRIDE`},R:null}}},{id:`L12_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`사장님, 곧 예정된 면접 시간입니다.`,JPN:`社長、もうすぐ予定していた面接のお時間です。`,ENG:`Boss, it's almost time for the interviews.`,TWN:`老闆，快到面試時間了。`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_IDLE`},R:null}}},{id:`L13_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`그런데……. 문제가 한 가지 생겼어요.`,JPN:`でも……一つ問題があります。`,ENG:`But... there has been a slight issue.`,TWN:`不過……現在有點問題。`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_DESPAIR`},R:null}}},{id:`L14_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`미나 양 때문인가?`,JPN:`ミナ君のことか？`,ENG:`Is it because of Mina?`,TWN:`是因為米娜的關係嗎？`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_DESPAIR`},R:null}}},{id:`L15_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:null,text:{KOREA:`문제라니?`,JPN:`問題？`,ENG:`An issue?`,TWN:`什麼問題？`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_DESPAIR`},R:null}}},{id:`L16_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`네. 역시 짐작하고 계셨군요.`,JPN:`はい。やっぱりご存じでしたか。`,ENG:`Yes. So you are already aware.`,TWN:`對，老闆也有發現到嗎？`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_DESPAIR`},R:null}}},{id:`L18_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`미나 씨가 충원을 원하지 않는다고 해서요.`,JPN:`ヒルデ小隊長が<color=#ffd34c>指示に従える奴がいれば構わん</color>とおっしゃられたので募集を出したのですが、`,ENG:`Commander Hilde said she <color=#ffd34c>"doesn't care as long as that person can follow orders,"</color> so I posted the recruitment notice,`,TWN:`希爾德小隊長說<color=#ffd34c>只要能聽從指令就好，其他無所謂</color>。所以我還特地寫在徵才內容上呢。`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_DESPAIR`},R:null}}},{id:`L19_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`힐데 소대장님께서 <color=#ffd34c>지시에 따를 수 있는 녀석이 있으면 상관없다</color>고 하시길래 공고를 올렸는데, 어떡할까요?`,JPN:`ミナさんが新しい人を迎えたくないと言うんです。どうしましょうか？`,ENG:`but Mina doesn't seem to want a new member. What should we do?`,TWN:`但米娜說她不希望徵人進來，怎麼辦才好？`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_IDLE`},R:null}}},{id:`L21_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`USER_ADMIN_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`흐음. 힐데 소대장의 조건도 난제이긴 하지만….`,JPN:`ふむ。ヒルデ小隊長の条件も難題だが……`,ENG:`Hmm. Commander Hilde’s condition is also a conundrum...`,TWN:`嗯嗯，希爾德小隊長的條件是有點難度，不過…`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_IDLE`},R:null}}},{id:`L22_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`USER_ADMIN_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`미나 양도 정신적으로 많이 지쳐 있는 모양이군.`,JPN:`ミナ君も精神的にだいぶ疲れているようだな。`,ENG:`And Mina also seems to be mentally exhausted.`,TWN:`米娜的精神狀況似乎不太好。`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_IDLE`},R:null}}},{id:`L25_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`USER_ADMIN_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`음? 바깥이 소란스러운 것 같은데?`,JPN:`うん？　外が騒がしいが。`,ENG:`Hmm? Why is it so loud out there?`,TWN:`嗯？外面在吵什麼？`},stage:{bg:`TRAINING`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`KIMHANA_COFFIN_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_SURPRISE`},R:null}}}];export{e as default};